1.8.0
=====

* The Almond platform was updated to 1.8. This brings a host of
  new features, including better support for question answering.

1.7.0
=====

* The Almond platform was updated to 1.7. This brings a host of
  new features, including better and more robust natural language.
* Developer mode now supports loading devices that are not in
  Thingpedia at all.

1.6.3
=====

* Expanded developer mode to allow loading local devices [#2]

1.6.2
=====

* Removed dependency on posix library, which is incompatible with node 12
* Updated dependencies

1.6.1
=====

* Updated depedencies

1.6.0
=====

* Update Almond platform to 1.6

1.5.0
=====

* Bump version to 1.5.0 to match the rest of the Almond platform
* Update dependencies

1.1.0
=====

* Update dependencies

1.0.0
=====

* First public release
